a compressor for compressing air;  
a combustion chamber for burning compression air exhausted from said compressor and fuel;   
a gas turbine driven by gas turbine exhaust gas from said combustion chamber;   
a recirculation path for recirculating a part of said gas turbine exhaust gas to an intake of said compressor;   
